    <item>
      <title>英国公投结果不佳 斯塔默指责苏纳克涉嫌税务欺诈</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-05/starmer-accuses-sunak-of-lying-with-tax-attack-as-uk-vote-sours</link>
      <description><![CDATA[工党领袖基尔·斯塔默 (Keir Starmer) 指责里希·苏纳克 (Rishi Sunak)“故意撒谎”，此前首相利用英国大选活动的第一场电视辩论声称其在民意调查中领先的竞争对手正计划加税。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-05/starmer-accuses-sunak-of-lying-with-tax-attack-as-uk-vote-sours</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 05 Jun 2024 15:54:32 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
